<span id="freeTextContainer17567454761868972265">Another great Koontz novel. I had expected Seize the Night to be very similar to its prequel, Fear Nothing. However, Seize the Night was even more suspenseful and driven than its predecessor. The end absolutely floored me. Completely unexpected and brilliant! </span>

